-- Ford sales rise 2 percent in July
-- 
-- Mon Aug 3, 2009 11:11am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/08/03/us-ford-shares-idUSTRE5723HE20090803

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Ford Motor Co shares held their gains, up 6.6 percent at $8.53, on Monday after the automaker said total sales for July rose 2 percent versus the year-ago period. 

 (Reporting by  Chuck Mikolajczak , Editing by Chizu Nomiyama)